  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Cold-Start-Problem-Andrew-Chen/dp/0062969749&quot;&gt;The Cold Start Problem: How to Start and Scale Network Effects&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
